      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Selection of turbulence and hemolysis sub-models must be documented with literature justification; sensitivity analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-ω turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model were selected based on published FDA pump benchmark comparisons. Model-form sensitivity analysis is scoped out as not required at MRL 2."
    },
