      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary condition values must be traceable to published sources or direct measurement; uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Fluid density, viscosity coefficients, and hemolysis model constants are traceable to peer-reviewed sources cited in the simulation report. Formal uncertainty propagation through model inputs is scoped out at MRL 2."
