    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieve their required levels under MRL 2. The six factors scoped out are appropriately excluded per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 at this model risk level. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The assessment team accepts the model for use in the regulatory submission.",
